psalm.text:
[[Dn 3,68]]Dew and rain, bless the Lord;
praise and exalt him above all forever.
[[Dn 3,69]]Frost and chill, bless the Lord;
praise and exalt him above all forever.
[[Dn 3,70]]Ice and snow, bless the Lord;
praise and exalt him above all forever.
[[Dn 3,71]]Nights and days, bless the Lord;
praise and exalt him above all forever.
[[Dn 3,72]]Light and darkness, bless the Lord;
praise and exalt him above all forever.
[[Dn 3,73]]Lightnings and clouds, bless the Lord;
praise and exalt him above all forever.
[[Dn 3,74]]Let the earth bless the Lord,
praise and exalt him above all forever.
